Gross sales:
number of products * sale price
Gross Sales = SUMX(financials,financials[Units Sold]*financials[Sale Price])

----------
Net sales:
gross sales - discounts
Net Sales = [Gross Sales]-[Total Discounts]

----------
Cost of goods sold:
unit sold * manufacturing price
Cost of Goods Sold = SUMX(financials,financials[Units Sold]*financials[Manufacturing Price])

----------

Total Profit;
Total Profit = [Net Sales]-[Cost of Goods Sold]
